788
00:34:22,128 --> 00:34:23,195
(grunts)

789
00:34:23,229 --> 00:34:24,530
Get up.

790
00:34:26,598 --> 00:34:28,567
(crowd groans)

791
00:34:31,270 --> 00:34:33,405
What am I doing?

792
00:34:33,439 --> 00:34:35,141
Fight me.

793
00:34:35,174 --> 00:34:36,542
No.

794
00:34:36,575 --> 00:34:39,845
You see, I won't
stoop down to your level.

795
00:34:41,513 --> 00:34:44,250
Because I am
better than you are.

796
00:34:44,283 --> 00:34:47,486
(crowd jeering)

797
00:34:50,322 --> 00:34:51,590
(Lucifer grunts)

798
00:34:51,623 --> 00:34:53,625
Fight me!

799
00:34:58,330 --> 00:35:00,266
(stammers)

800
00:35:02,401 --> 00:35:03,735
Winner by submission!

801
00:35:03,769 --> 00:35:06,104
(crowd cheering and jeering)

802
00:35:09,841 --> 00:35:12,878
It's been, like,
two hours, Chloe.

803
00:35:12,911 --> 00:35:15,181
I seriously doubt
Tio Sorrento's gonna show up.

804
00:35:15,214 --> 00:35:16,615
Especially now that
he knows he's a suspect

805
00:35:16,648 --> 00:35:17,616
in Aiden Scott's murder.

806
00:35:17,649 --> 00:35:18,784
He swore to Charlotte Richards

807
00:35:18,817 --> 00:35:20,619
that he had nothing to do
with the murder

808
00:35:20,652 --> 00:35:21,820
and that he'd help us
find the killer.

809
00:35:21,853 --> 00:35:24,756
So he's just gonna drop a bunch
of cash off into a locker?

810
00:35:24,790 --> 00:35:26,525
Yeah, if that's what's gonna
clear his name.

811
00:35:26,558 --> 00:35:27,759
And whoever picks it up

812
00:35:27,793 --> 00:35:29,628
either killed Aiden Scott
or knows who did.

813
00:35:29,661 --> 00:35:31,663
And if you're wrong?

814
00:35:31,697 --> 00:35:32,898
Tio doesn't show up,

815
