847
00:37:01,052 --> 00:37:02,421
Wait.

848
00:37:02,454 --> 00:37:03,755
That was you in the street?

849
00:37:03,789 --> 00:37:05,324
H-How'd we get here?

850
00:37:05,357 --> 00:37:06,191
We flew.

851
00:37:06,224 --> 00:37:07,759
Thought we needed
a bit of privacy.

852
00:37:07,793 --> 00:37:09,695
Who are you?

853
00:37:09,728 --> 00:37:11,363
And you, I-I-I shot you.

854
00:37:12,298 --> 00:37:13,432
And yet
he's standing here alive.

855
00:37:13,465 --> 00:37:15,267
It's shocking, isn't it?

856
00:37:15,301 --> 00:37:17,803
Look, I-I don't want
any trouble.

857
00:37:17,836 --> 00:37:19,671
I'll get you a new necklace.

858
00:37:19,705 --> 00:37:20,806
No, see, I want mine.

859
00:37:20,839 --> 00:37:22,874
It's just a necklace.
What's the big deal about it?

860
00:37:22,908 --> 00:37:25,477
Because my father gave it to me!

861
00:37:25,511 --> 00:37:26,678
