Look.

862
00:37:26,712 --> 00:37:29,047
Taking the necklace
wasn't part of my plan.

863
00:37:29,080 --> 00:37:31,950
So you planned to
kill the other human?

864
00:37:31,983 --> 00:37:34,453
No, that was a mistake, too.

865
00:37:34,486 --> 00:37:35,754
Aiden was like a son to me.

866
00:37:35,787 --> 00:37:38,557
I got into some money trouble.
I thought of a fix.

867
00:37:38,590 --> 00:37:39,691
Aiden throws his fight.

868
00:37:39,725 --> 00:37:43,462
We bet on it,
take home a huge payday.

869
00:37:43,495 --> 00:37:44,630
Both of us.

870
00:37:44,663 --> 00:37:47,399
But the fighter didn't want
to play his part, did he?

871
00:37:47,433 --> 00:37:49,901
He said he'd rather walk away
from it than throw it.

872
00:37:49,935 --> 00:37:51,570
I went to try to scare him,

873
00:37:51,603 --> 00:37:52,704
but Aiden fought back.

874
00:37:52,738 --> 00:37:56,041
I panicked, I shot him.

875
00:37:56,074 --> 00:37:58,544
Tried to make it look
like a robbery.

876
00:37:58,577 --> 00:37:59,945
That's when I saw you.

877
00:37:59,978 --> 00:38:01,947
I-I didn't know
what you'd seen, I'm sorry.

878
00:38:01,980 --> 00:38:04,616
I'm gonna ask you
for the last time.

879
00:38:04,650 --> 00:38:06,552
Where...

880
00:38:06,585 --> 00:38:08,086
is my necklace?

881
00:38:08,119 --> 00:38:10,356
It's in the gym.

882
00:38:10,389 --> 00:38:11,457
It's in my safe.

883
00:38:11,490 --> 00:38:14,092
Let's go drop him
back at the beach.

884
00:38:14,125 --> 00:38:16,728
Just a moment.

885
00:38:16,762 --> 00:38:19,665
So you killed
your so-called "son"

886
00:38:19,698 --> 00:38:21,533
