to play a part

887
00:38:21,567 --> 00:38:23,034
in your plan.

888
00:38:23,068 --> 00:38:25,771
Now, that is just pure evil.

889
00:38:25,804 --> 00:38:28,840
And I should know.

890
00:38:28,874 --> 00:38:32,378
Because I am the King of Evil.

891
00:38:34,079 --> 00:38:35,647
