I-I killed Aiden Scott.

898
00:38:45,657 --> 00:38:46,858
I'm sorry,
it's-it's all my fault.

899
00:38:46,892 --> 00:38:48,794
I... I killed him.

900
00:38:48,827 --> 00:38:51,897
Sounds like
a confession to me.

901
00:38:54,700 --> 00:38:56,468
Looks like your gamble paid off.

902
00:38:56,502 --> 00:38:58,069
(handcuffs clicking)

903
00:39:05,176 --> 00:39:08,013
