Luci, why are we back here?

904
00:39:08,046 --> 00:39:10,382
It's time for
us to leave.

905
00:39:10,416 --> 00:39:12,984
We've been here on
Earth long enough.

906
00:39:13,018 --> 00:39:17,022
Yes, you see, that's what
I wanted to talk to you about.

907
00:39:17,055 --> 00:39:18,624
(sighs)

908
00:39:18,657 --> 00:39:19,758
I'm not leaving.

909
00:39:19,791 --> 00:39:21,627
(chuckles softly)

910
00:39:21,660 --> 00:39:22,994
