to seek His approval.

919
00:39:48,654 --> 00:39:51,022
Still playing a part
in His play.

920
00:39:52,724 --> 00:39:54,926
Well, no more, Brother.

921
00:39:54,960 --> 00:39:59,565
He abandoned me,
so why shouldn't I abandon Him?

922
00:39:59,598 --> 00:40:03,735
It's time I fully accept
how everyone else sees me:

923
00:40:03,769 --> 00:40:05,837
