929
00:40:17,983 --> 00:40:19,651
You are coming back
to Hell with me.

930
00:40:19,685 --> 00:40:21,219
There's no discussion.

931
00:40:21,252 --> 00:40:23,589
(sighs)

932
00:40:23,622 --> 00:40:26,492
Yes, you see...

933
00:40:26,525 --> 00:40:28,494
